[TITLE]
PRV and PSV in series — exercises both valve types simultaneously

[JUNCTIONS]
J1    0    20
J2    0    10
J3    0    10
J4    0    15

[RESERVOIRS]
R1    200

[PIPES]
P1    R1    J1    500    12    100    0    Open
P2    J2    J3    300    12    100    0    Open
P3    J4    J1    800    12    100    0    Open

[VALVES]
; PRV limits downstream pressure to 50 psi
PRV1    J1    J2    12    PRV    50    0
; PSV sustains upstream pressure at 30 psi
PSV1    J3    J4    12    PSV    30    0

[OPTIONS]
Units    GPM
Headloss    H-W
Accuracy    0.0001

[END]
